           	<td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white">
                      <font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Well let me start off by saying this is only a work in progress so please add all your comments below.<br /><br />I have been raiding for a long time now and it has always troubled me that every raid leader seems to think that I am only a mana battery and just use most necros to feed clerics. With that said let me also say that I am only 59th level and these calculations are based on MY mana pool and MY spells and keep in mind that as I get higher in levels the spells do more damage over time.<br /><br />Ok acording to magelo I have 2922 mana and 1112 Hp. OK lets do a bit of math. I have no FT items so I will only be using lich form. ok so I gain 20m a tick using this and with all my regen up and if I get a regrowth I loose no HP. So over 2min I get 400m back do to lich form. Now with Sedulous Subversion I give a person 150mana for 400 of my mana. If I am liched up I get about 3300 mana over 2 min total. Ok over that 2min I can cast Sedulous 8 times before I am all out of mana so that gives the person 1200mana.<br />Now looking at the CH spell that clerics get costs them 400m ( This is the 7500hp one) so they will get a total of 3 more CH casts before they are also tapped out. Now keep this in mind.<br /><br />OK now for some stats on necro damage spells:<br /><br />Ces of Cor does 1000hp dam in 1min plus and AC and str debuff for 250m<br />Vexing Mordania does 1094 over 54 sec for 495m<br />Pyrocuror does 1998 dam over 1min 48sec for 400m<br />Devouring Darkness does 1599dam over 1min 18sec for 400m<br />Touch of night does 720dd dam for 405 mana.<br /><br />So lets take a looksy at this:<br /><br />My mana pool with lich up is 3300 over 2min.<br /><br />During this 2 min I could cast:<br /><br />Ces of Cor 1000hp<br />Vex           1094hp<br />Pyrocuror   1998hp<br />Darkness   1599hp<br /><br />Total of 5491dam over 2min for a total of 1645 mana. <br /><br />Now I can actually recast these each for a grand total of 10982dam over 4min and still have another 410mana left.<br /><br />I think that this math right here shows that our mana might be better used as a damage dealer than as a mana battery. I think we need to put the word out that we are more than just a portable mana supply.<br /><br />Just my opinion.<br /><br />Gil<br /><br />Pain is temporary<br />Death is forever</span id="msg"></font>
           	</td>
                    </tr>
